{% set version = "2022.07.2+576" %}

package:
  name: rstudio
  version: {{ pkg_version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/archive/refs/tags/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 55705c36a9b826064b4d9aa87b58c40bb9f7cd2f149b16d554e20136306ce301
  patches:
    - 0001-fix-soci.patch
    - 0002-no-static-linking.patch

build:
  number: {{ upstream_build_num + build }}
  skip: true  # [win]
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/rstudio/lib
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - make
    - cmake
    - ant
    - yarn
    - wget
    - ripgrep
    - coreutils  # [osx]
    - patchelf  # [linux]
    - unzip
    - nodejs 14
    - {{ cdt('mesa-libgl-devel') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('mesa-dri-drivers') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libselinux') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxdamage') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxxf86vm') }}  # [linux]
    - {{ cdt('libxext') }}     # [linux]

outputs:
  - name: rstudio-desktop
    script: build-desktop.sh
    build:
      skip: true  # [win]
      rpaths:
        - lib/R/lib/
        - lib/rstudio/lib
        - lib/
    requirements:
      build:
        - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
